snippet.title: Joe Exotic Deposition   Truth About Carole Baskin   Litigation IQ
snippet.description:
How to dress for a deposition - A non-descript polo – and no hat – would have worked for a guy like Joe Exotic. Be yourself but be professional. 
How to answer deposition questions:
Don't repeat the question out loud. Repeat it internally if needed.
Don't answer too quickly. 
Don't flip through documents while being asked a question. 
Don't editorialize.


For an analysis of Joe's Deposition mistakes, read this blog post: https://www.litigationiq.com/post/joe-exotic-deposition-what-not-to-do
